data.description: Are you looking for a home that has been tastefully updated with an abundance of room to grow, if yes this is the home for you! Located in a well sought out area, this 5 bedroom, 2 master suite, 3 full bath home is the perfect one to call yours. New carpet in the bedrooms, new LVP in the main living and kitchen, and tile floors in the bathrooms. The main living space is finished off with lovely crown molding and chair rail. Newer roof installed in 2020, both upstairs and downstairs HVAC recently replaced- 2018 and 2019. All appliances convey. Bathrooms have been updated, kitchen updated, and new granite installed. The downstairs master offers 2 closets and a private master bath. The upstairs master is huge, a MUST SEE, and guaranteed to fit your needs. The upstairs bath has double vanities w/ plenty of room. Tons of storage between the closets, utility room, and attic. The back yard has a nice deck surrounded by a peaceful atmosphere, but also a short driving distance to major cities.
